name: Empathy
description: This piece is my very first piece since the start of my official art career. It represents the relationship between lovers. It shows a man, in a hectic emotional state, being cradled by the one he loves. She, however, has a calm presence and face that brings serenity to his chaos. Almost like a guardian angel of sorts, that protects him for the surrounding cloud of chaos. Which also doubles as a chaotic crowd fueled by negativity.
